<emphasis id="703890CD76295960DF1573400834C147" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="49">A, B, D</emphasis>
by J.L. Clark &amp; 
<emphasis id="EFDA1563DCA3C160C51276DEDEFA3781" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="49">C, E</emphasis>
